snippet.title: Big Buck HD Arcade Quick Preview
snippet.description: http://arcadeheroes.com - Just a brief look over the latest coin-op arcade game from Raw THrills and Play Mechanix, Big Buck HD. This is available in July 2012. Sorry about the lack of sound for the first 27 seconds, no idea why that happened. ALL machines are online enabled so they are really pushing that along with all the features it offers, which I was not able to really get into. I will be able to do so later on so stay tuned.
